{
  "stem": "11144.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he told us that what had happened with my father, my father went to look for us to these people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, he had the same experience as us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he went back to the apartment, went under the bed, and hid himself under the bed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He survived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He survived the cleaning out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at night, I think some Ukrainians or Poles came in to rob the apartment, and they found him there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they called the Germans, and the Germans took him back to the-- they brought him back to the mass grave, and he was killed there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was tough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a lot of bickering and a lot of jealousy and a lot of-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] it was tough.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was tough.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, the people that were in the apartment originally had a little bit more, I guess, power, or they thought they had more power--",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--right, than the people that were brought in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was very tough because, you know, people were stealing food because the food was so scarce, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so it-- it was-- it was tough.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you know, there you couldn't-- I mean, there were no bathrooms, so we had to go outside and shower outside.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I think there were outhouses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the hygiene wasn't the greatest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember once laying in bed, and I didn't feel like getting up next morning.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said to myself that-- the incidents, you somehow remember some.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'm laying in bed, I said, oh, I hope I'm sick today.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I hope I get sick so I don't have to get up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't have to face the world.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't-- but what do you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
